column1: # flag = feature flag which is supposed to be checked for filter.
#          1. DEFINED = Remove the code inside "#ifdef flag" and keep the #else part.
#          2. NOT_DEFINED = Remove the code inside "#ifndef flag" and keep the #else part.
# New filters are required to be added in new lines.
# Spaces are not allowed between comma separated values. e.g. entry <FLAG
column2: DEFINED> will throw error because of space before "DEFINED".
